dct_title_s: Map of wonderful Copenhagen and North Zealand
dct_description_sm: Tourist Association of Copenhagen. Index of tourist attractions and points of interest on margin. Selected buildings are illustrated. Verso: map of North Zealand at [ca. 1:342,100] and Buses Copnehagen at [ca. 1:76,900]; in margins: advertisements and directory of resorts. 1972
